/li><li>74,050 euros for a single person with one dependant, to be increased by 4,150 euros per additional dependant.</li></ul></li></ul><p>The amount decreases the longer one receives an allowance.</p><h3>Payments</h3><p>The allowance is paid monthly directly to your credit institution.</p><p>You can get an allowance <strong>for a maximum of 36</strong> months. If there is an interruption in the period of unemployment or incapacity for work, the different periods are added up.</p><p>In case of <strong>involuntary unemployment</strong>, you are entitled to the allowances for a maximum of <strong>18 consecutive months</strong>. To qualify for a subsequent period of allowances, you must again have worked full-time or part-time for at least 3 months.</p><p>The end date of the insurance policy does not affect the period of relief. These are two separate terms. As long as the insurance term runs (maximum 10 years), you can apply for the allowance, but it is perfectly possible that you will still receive the monthly allowance when the end date of the policy has passed, as long as the conditions are met.</p>","fr":"Financieel voordeel","nl-BE-x-formal":"Financieel voordeel","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Financieel voordeel","de":"Financieel voordeel"},"@type":"FinancieelVoordeel","order":0}],"creatie":"2009-08-25T08:22:36Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2024-01-12T14:44:37Z","laatstOntvangen":"2024-07-18T12:25:36.373914805Z","productnummer":"185","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"en-x-generated":"<p>Flemish Housing Fund<br>Department of Insurance Guaranteed Housing<br>Ieperlaan 41<br>1000 Brussels</p><p>telephone: 02 548 92 39 (available every morning between 8.30 a.m. and 12 noon, except Thursday)<br>e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be\">vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be</a></p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","en":"See also on vlaanderen.be"},"url":"https://