g en heeft dus niets te maken met een hospitalisatieverzekering of andere aanvullende verzekeringen die mutualiteiten aanbieden.</p>","en":"<p>The Flemish Social Protection (Dutch: ‘Vlaamse Sociale Bescherming’) offers financial assistance to people requiring long-term care.</p><p>The Flemish Social Protection differs from the health insurance, which refunds medical costs and is provided by the health insurance funds. The Flemish Social Protection also has nothing to do with a hospitalization insurance or other additional insurances offered by the health insurance funds.<br>More information is available on the website of the <a href=\"https://www.vlaamsesocialebescherming.be\">Flemish Social Protection</a> (available in Dutch only).</p>"},"publicatiekanalen":["YourEurope"],"type":"FinancieleVerplichting","themas":["WelzijnGezondheid"],"doelgroepen":["Burger","Onderneming","Organisatie"],"geografischToepassingsgebieden":["BE1","BE2"],"yourEuropeCategorieen":["GezondheidszorgZiekteverzekering"],"regelgevingTekst":{"fr":"<p>Décret du 30 mars 1999: décret portant organisation de assurance soins.</p>","nl":"<p>Decreet 18 mei 2018 houdende de Vlaamse sociale bescherming.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Decreet 18 mei 2018 houdende de Vlaamse sociale bescherming.</p>","en-x-generated":"<p>Decree 18 May 2018 governing Flemish social protection.</p>","nl-BE-x-formal":"<p>Decreet 18 mei 2018 houdende de Vlaamse sociale bescherming.</p>","en":"<p>Decree of 30 March 1999: concerning the organisation of the care insurance</p>"},"uitzonderingen":{"fr":"<p>Les travailleurs frontaliers et employés des organisations internationales doivent uniquement s’affilier dans certains cas.</p>","en":"<p>Cross-border workers and international organization’s employees only have to join in some cases.</p>"},"zoektermen":{"nl":["aansluiten","aansluiting","bijdrage","ledenbijdrage","niet-medische kosten","premie","tegemoetkoming","tenlasteneming","uitkering","verzekering","wonen","ziekteverz